{"type": "article", "id": 5912, "title": "Industrial Facility W152 台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-05T07:54:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233822HlvqDeZBgYkIT9Ej.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞典照明品牌 Wästberg 首次联手伦敦设计工作室 Industrial Facility 推出了一款 LED 台灯作品 Industrial Facility W152 Lamp，它既可以放置在桌面，也可以悬挂在墙面或是其他平整的表面。这款台灯能够利用 3 个 USB 接口，智能检测出针对各种电子设备所需要的充电模式，并且用最快的速度为电子设备供给电力。W152 拥有坚固的铝合金灯体，尽管外形小巧，但却能够提供多达 3 安培的电力，足以为笔记本电脑补充电量。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233821wD2jhQzvVoIRgrNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233821S2RkyB0JGLp8ZWrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233822jAfIdeNUwzYnWlur.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}